- `_chat.settings.tsx` - Settings page
- `routeTree.gen.ts` - Auto-generated route tree (TanStack Router)

---

### 4. CSS & STYLING ARCHITECTURE

**Location:** `apps/web/src/index.css`

**Tailwind CSS Setup:**
```css
