**Design Tokens:**
- Color palette: background, foreground, primary, secondary, accent, destructive, info, success, warning, muted
- Border radius: sm, md, lg, xl, 2xl, 3xl, 4xl (calculated from --radius base)
- Shadows: xs, xs/5 (using new shadow syntax)
